HEADWORD: Homœomorphism
<hw>Ho`m⟦oe⟧*o*mor"phism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Hom⟦oe⟧omorphous</er>.]</ety> <def>A near similarity of crystalline
